📁 js/
├── main.js            ← Entry point, app initialization
├── api.js             ← All API functions (fetch, post, uploadImage, etc.)
├── dom.js             ← DOM handlers: alerts, loading, resetForm, image preview
├── dynamic.js         ← Dynamic cast/crew/clip section handlers
├── modal.js           ← Modal logic for cast/crew
├── submit.js          ← Final form submission + validation
